{
  "stem": "26142.17",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you cut out the hole for the head here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the bag was-- so we pull those bags under the shirt in order to-- to preserve some body heat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because in-- in-- in-- with the-- from the cement bags, at least the-- the-- the wind-- the wind wouldn't-- wouldn't dissipate the body heat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But one day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was so lucky that day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Some-- some grandma above in heaven intervened for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Guys came in, and the kapo noticed that they had these cement bags-- they were empty cement bags that were thrown away-- under there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They beat the guy up so bad that he died next day, for that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was able to get out from the barrack into the outhouse and get rid of that bag.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't know how-- how-- who-- who saved me from-- from-- from that terrible crime that I committed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Anyway, it came to the point that I couldn't go on anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said, I'm going to register sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When I registered sick, the only thing what they looked, if you had swollen legs, if you were swollen, you know, the legs down here, what were swollen, then they took you in.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The-- the doctor took me in, in the-- in the revier in the evening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I-- I had this-- besides that my leg was swollen, this was frozen, and it got swollen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I couldn't even take my shoe off anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So he said, yeah, in the morning-- in the morning, you will be operated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He took us in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I got into the revier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was very clean in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The conditions in there were the same bunk beds, the same narrow as before, three high.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
